N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 73.6 - Industrial board of appeals subject matter list

State Regulations

The Industrial Board of Appeals shall maintain a subject
matter list of records required to be disclosed by article 6 of the Public

Officers Law, and such subject matter list shall be located in the offices of
the Industrial Board of Appeals in Albany. Notes
